comments: Thesis (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Middleton's (MIL) path.
Lopez (MIL) makes marginal contact with Tatum's (BOS) body after the release of his shot and does not affect his ability to follow through.
Tatum (BOS) briefly places a hand to DiVincenzo's (MIL) side as he dribbles.
Tatum (BOS) extends his leg and makes marginal foot to foot contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that he moves through during the drive to the basket.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of an offensive foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL) is overturned to a shooting foul on Smart (BOS).  Smart was not established in a legal guarding position at the time of Antetokounmpo's gather on the driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental contact with Brown's (BOS) arm after the release that does not affect his ability to follow through.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) engages and disengages with Smart (BOS) off ball.
Smart (BOS) legally contest Middleton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) makes contact with Brown's (BOS) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engage as Smart places his hand to Antetokoumpo's back momentarily and removes it.
Tatum (BOS) briefly places an arm around Antetokounmpo (MIL) during the pick, but immediately removes it.
Thesis (BOS) makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm during the play at the basket.
Tatum's (BOS) off-arm naturally separates from his body as he steps back from the defender and he does not deliver contact to Matthews (MIL) at the end of the drive.
Hayward (BOS) makes slight contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) off-arm that does not affect his SQBR.
Tatum (BOS) places a hand to DiVincenzo's (MIL) backside during the play at the basket.
Theis (BOS) makes contact with the ball after the made basket, preventing MIL from immediately inbounding.
Hayward (BOS) commits a take foul on Hill (MIL).
